As the day progresses, interview sign-up sheets fill with names, and a startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session. Concurrently, workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom, with consulting firms contributing to the atmosphere by stacking glossy case study booklets on high tables. As the fair approaches its end, announcement chimes signal the final hour of the event.

Groups of friends actively mark target employers on the event map, indicating their interest in specific companies, while some friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly. Human resources teams jot notes on tablets as students introduce themselves. Dozens of booths with colorful banners surround the polished floor, contributing to the vibrant atmosphere of the event, where students also compare swag items like water bottles and phone chargers. A welcome announcement outlines the fair schedule over the PA system, and announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair. Additionally, international students queue for advice on visa sponsorship requirements.
